@startuml
title Feature 010. Оформление заказа и дозаказ. Sequence diagram

actor "Покупатель/Партнер" as User
participant "Frontend web-shell\n/order, /order/supplementary" as FE
participant "module_order\nOrderController" as OrderApi
participant "module_order\nCheckoutService" as Checkout
participant "module_cart\nCart API" as Cart
participant "module_catalog\nCampaign/Product API" as Catalog
participant "Benefit rules" as Benefit
participant "Delivery integration" as Delivery
participant "WMS/1C inventory" as Wms
participant "Payment provider" as Payment
participant "Audit/Event publisher" as Audit

User -> FE: opens /order or /order/supplementary
FE -> OrderApi: POST /api/order/checkouts\ncartId, checkoutType, Idempotency-Key
OrderApi -> Checkout: startCheckout(command)
Checkout -> Cart: validateCart(cartId, checkoutType, owner)
Cart --> Checkout: cart snapshot, totals, availability, validation
Checkout -> Catalog: resolve campaign and product snapshots
Catalog --> Checkout: campaign/product data
Checkout -> Benefit: precheck role, partner, VIP/super, retention limits
Benefit --> Checkout: allowed benefits and warnings
Checkout -> Audit: CHECKOUT_STARTED
Checkout --> OrderApi: CheckoutDraftResponse
OrderApi --> FE: checkout draft with STR_MNEMO_* reasons

User -> FE: enters recipient and contacts
FE -> OrderApi: PUT /api/order/checkouts/{id}/recipient
OrderApi -> Checkout: updateRecipient
Checkout -> Audit: RECIPIENT_UPDATED or VALIDATION_FAILED
Checkout --> FE: updated draft

User -> FE: selects address or pickup point
FE -> OrderApi: PUT /api/order/checkouts/{id}/address
OrderApi -> Checkout: updateAddress
Checkout -> Delivery: calculate options(address, items, checkoutType)
Delivery --> Checkout: delivery options and reasonMnemo
Checkout -> Audit: ADDRESS_UPDATED
Checkout --> FE: draft with deliveryOptions

User -> FE: selects delivery
FE -> OrderApi: PUT /api/order/checkouts/{id}/delivery
OrderApi -> Checkout: selectDelivery
Checkout -> Delivery: verify selected method
Delivery --> Checkout: available or STR_MNEMO_ORDER_DELIVERY_UNAVAILABLE
Checkout -> Audit: DELIVERY_SELECTED or VALIDATION_FAILED
Checkout --> FE: updated draft and totals

User -> FE: applies wallet/cashback/catalog benefits
FE -> OrderApi: PUT /api/order/checkouts/{id}/benefits\nIdempotency-Key
OrderApi -> Checkout: applyBenefits
Checkout -> Benefit: validate limits and calculate amounts
Benefit --> Checkout: applied/rejected benefits
Checkout -> Audit: BENEFIT_APPLIED or VALIDATION_FAILED
Checkout --> FE: recalculated draft

User -> FE: selects payment method
FE -> OrderApi: PUT /api/order/checkouts/{id}/payment\nIdempotency-Key
OrderApi -> Checkout: selectPayment
Checkout -> Payment: create or reuse payment session
Payment --> Checkout: paymentSessionId, paymentStatus
Checkout -> Audit: PAYMENT_SELECTED
Checkout --> FE: draft with payment status

User -> FE: confirms checkout
FE -> OrderApi: POST /api/order/checkouts/{id}/confirm\ncheckoutVersion, Idempotency-Key
OrderApi -> Checkout: confirmCheckout
Checkout -> Cart: final validation
Checkout -> Benefit: final benefit validation
Checkout -> Wms: reserve items
alt full reserve
  Wms --> Checkout: reservation ids
  Checkout -> Payment: ensure payment session
  Payment --> Checkout: payment status
  Checkout -> Audit: ORDER_CONFIRMED
  Checkout -> Audit: publish order event for assembly/delivery
  Checkout --> OrderApi: OrderConfirmationResponse\norderNumber, nextAction
  OrderApi --> FE: success result
  FE --> User: order number and next payment step
else partial reserve
  Wms --> Checkout: available quantities and reason
  Checkout -> Audit: RESERVATION_FAILED
  Checkout --> OrderApi: validation response\nSTR_MNEMO_ORDER_PARTIAL_RESERVE
  OrderApi --> FE: controlled blocking state
  FE --> User: fix quantity or return to cart
else payment failed
  Payment --> Checkout: FAILED/EXPIRED
  Checkout -> Audit: PAYMENT_STATUS_CHANGED
  Checkout --> OrderApi: order/payment state\nSTR_MNEMO_ORDER_PAYMENT_FAILED
  OrderApi --> FE: retry payment state
  FE --> User: retry or change payment method
end
@enduml
